<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />Yahweh watches over all those who love him,</para>

<para style="q1">but he will destroy all the wicked.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />My mouth will speak out the praise of Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">let all mankind bless his holy name forever and ever.</para>
